snippet.title: MUSESTRUCK - DEMO TRAILER
snippet.description:
A 2D Platformer RPG about art and magic. You play as JOURNEY and QUINN, two young artist friends who explore a mysterious magical world called NEGATIVE SPACE, to try and make it back home.

WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3491470/MUSESTRUCK/
JOIN THE DISCORD: https://discord.com/invite/tQBWhS5ZK3
FOLLOW ON BLUESKY: https://bsky.app/profile/brennangames.bsky.social
FOLLOW ON TWITTER: https://x.com/BrennanDraws
